query.sql:
1. - Destination database (to be duplicated)
Init.ora parameters
alter system set db_file_name_convert='+EUSDPRD_DATA_01/sdprd','/u02/oradata/SDDEV' scope=spfile sid='*';
alter system set log_file_name_convert='+EUSDPRD_FRA_01/sdprd','/u02/oradata/SDDEV','+EUSDPRD_FRA_01/sdprd','/u02/fast_recovery_area/SDDEV' scope=spfile sid='*';

Confirm the connectivity to the target database (SDPRD) from the host where auxiliary database (SDDEV) is
Shutdown destination (auxiliary) database and startup in NOMOUNT mode.

2. Rman duplicate script: rman_duplicate_SDPRD_to_SDDEV.rcv
spool log to rman_duplicate_SDPRD_to_SDDEV.log
# target is the source and auxiliary is destination
connect target sys/a7410sdprd@sdprd
connect auxiliary /

run {
allocate auxiliary channel d1 type disk format '/euclsp10/SDPRD/rman/181107/%U';
##Archivelog number get from sql archive log list command
set until sequence 71201;

#set until time "to_date('2018-11-07 13:00:00','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')";
duplicate target database to SDDEV nofilenamecheck
logfile
group 1('/u02/oradata/SDDEV/onlinelog/redo1a.log','/u02/fast_recovery_area/SDDEV/onlinelog/redo1b.log') size 100m,
group 2('/u02/oradata/SDDEV/onlinelog/redo2a.log','/u02/fast_recovery_area/SDDEV/onlinelog/redo2b.log') size 100m,
group 3('/u02/oradata/SDDEV/onlinelog/redo3a.log','/u02/fast_recovery_area/SDDEV/onlinelog/redo3b.log') size 100m;
}

Exit

3. After the database duplicate is completed shutdown and restart the db
4. YOU MAY need to drop and recreate TEMP file.
alter tablespace temp drop tempfile '/u02/oradata/SDDEV/tempfile/temp.260.821620521';

